8e7f634d0f9e12548e320206ab527622173f3b4ad0e860f428b2957baca54de2c7352ac3ae1a1eb37709a5c62f7ca3c882b975a5859c12c81ff1cf372e55fce3  cmake-add-insecure-suffix.patch
"
